  <div class='bold_text' style='width: 620px;'>
    RoadWorks is a 3-D interactive application that encapsulates the mathematics and
    engineering standards of roadway design, allowing the designer to focus on practical
    and aesthetic issues while manipulating a centerline alignment with the mouse. 
  </div>
  
